| famous pract    = [[Kisshomaru Ueshiba]], [[Moriteru Ueshiba]], [[Steven Seagal]], [[Christian Tissier]], [[Morihiro Saito]], [[Koichi Tohei]], [[Yoshimitsu Yamada]], [[Gozo Shioda]]
| parenthood      = ''[[Daitō-ryū Aiki-jūjutsu|Aiki-jūjutsu]]''; [[Jujutsu]]; ''[[Kenjutsu]]''; ''[[Sōjutsu]]'', ''[[Bojutsu]]'', ''[[Iaijutsu]]'', ''[[Jojutsu]]''
